WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.200
Hello. This is the Stream player caption demo.

00:00:04.200 --> 00:00:08.700
You can switch subtitle languages from the CC menu.

00:00:08.700 --> 00:00:13.500
Mute now drops the volume to zero and stores your last value.

00:00:13.500 --> 00:00:18.200
Unmute restores that previous volume automatically.
